    "description": "A roast you're sure to take a real shine to. You'll pop the beechwood smoked gammon in the oven, basted in a honey and treacle stout glaze, then carve thickly and serve with creamy mash and buttery Hispi cabbage. A proper plate of comfort with a touch of glamour.",
